data.description: Great opportunity to own this super cute ranch bungalow which includes a great 2 car garage that is not common on homes in the neighborhood. This home features 3 bedrooms & 1 bathroom with a great layout, huge living room, and situated on an oversized lot!! Newer carpet installed in 2021, newer vinyl flooring, newer hot water heater. This home is situated in a great little neighborhood close to shopping, great restaurants, & easy freeway access!
